# EmailJS Configuration (for email notifications)
# Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com/ (free tier: 200 emails/month)
#
# 1. Create an account at emailjs.com
# 2. Add an email service (Gmail, Outlook, etc.)
# 3. Create two email templates:
#    - Delivered template: Notify sender their dedication was delivered
#    - Viewed template: Notify sender their dedication was opened
# 4. Get your Public Key from Account > API Keys
#
# Template variables for DELIVERED template:
# - {{to_email}} - sender's email
# - {{recipient_name}} - recipient's name
# - {{recipient_instagram}} - recipient's Instagram
# - {{subject}} - email subject
#
# Template variables for VIEWED template:
# - {{to_email}} - sender's email
# - {{recipient_name}} - recipient's name
# - {{view_link}} - link to the dedication
# - {{subject}} - email subject

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key
VITE_EMAILJS_DELIVERED_TEMPLATE=your_delivered_template_id
VITE_EMAILJS_VIEWED_TEMPLATE=your_viewed_template_id
